in the benchmark suite are detected correctly.

\paragraph{Architecture complexity.}
The benchmarks range from 2-step SimpleLinear (24 Z3 queries) to
20-step DeepMLP-10 (297 Z3 queries).  The product theory generates
Z3 queries for all three domains ($\mathcal{T}_{\mathit{shape}}$,
$\mathcal{T}_{\mathit{device}}$, $\mathcal{T}_{\mathit{phase}}$)
plus cross-domain constraints at every computation step, totaling
1891 queries across all architectures in 4597\,ms.

\subsection{Contract Discovery Results}\label{sec:cegar-eval}

We evaluate the contract discovery loop on 8 benchmarks with implicit shape
contracts:

\begin{table}[t]
