VAE           & 2 & 1 & Safe & $\mu$.out = $\sigma$.out \\
ResNet-block  & 1 & 1 & Safe & skip dim = residual dim \\
U-Net-skip    & 3 & 1 & Safe & enc$_i$.out = dec$_i$.in \\
